title: AHS Apocalypse Episode 9 Review SPOILERS!!
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I'm so mad! Queenie and Zoe did not deserve to die like that!
This episode was WEAK SAUCE. Guess we're never going to find out what up with Timothy and Emily. Pissed. Ryan always starts what he can't finish. Except Asylum.
If the season finale is still in the past and nothing is answered at all I'm going to write a fanfic that fixes the fuckery of this season.
Still waiting for Fiona to come back at ep10, light herself a cigarette, drop a good line and then whoop some asses😂
Cordelia was astral projecting to the academy. Descensum is when you project to another dimension. You've failed the 7 Wonders test
